HR NO. 26 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, Incorporated,
Zeta Lambda Omega Chapter, on the occasion of its one hundred eighteenth Founders' Day
and seventy-first Charter Day; does hereby extend enduring appreciation for the chapter's
longstanding service to the citizens of Rapides Parish and the state of Louisiana; and does
hereby extend sincere wishes for the continued success of its members in their mission of
service to all mankind.
SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
